Text: According to IMDB, Explosions A to Z is s13e08, NOT s11e09 as you've stated. http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2413712/

Best guess is that this is S11E09. There's no official North American designation available for it but then this is the UK edit so who knows. There's supposedly 20 episodes (including specials) but I've only ever seen 8.

Sooooo.... assuming that S11E09 is correct the content matches the torrent title NOT the title in the description (which is probably a cut & paste error).
